short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enables Click-To-Dial from the chrome web-browser for Monmouth Telecom Hosted PBX Customers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Click-To-Dial Chrome extension is only applicable to Monmouth Telecom Hosted PBX Customers. This Add-On turns all telephone numbers on every web page into links.
